---
title: Wild Mushroom Ravioli with Grape Tomatoes, Zucchini, and Chili
description: This dish holds a special place in our pasta-loving hearts. We’ve swapped out ordinary ravioli for a wild mushroom variety, thrown in some juicy tomatoes (which happen to be at the peak of their season), and incorporated zucchini for a pop of green. It’s super easy, bursting with flavor, and almost too beautiful to eat.
